      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The exhaustion you see in them is a reflection of the burden you feel, and you're right, the math of it all seems impossibly heavy. But that 'logic' is a trap built from pain, and it doesn't account for the possibility of things shifting. Instead of ending the equation, imagine what it would take to change the variables—to find a different way to ease that weight. Please, reach out to a professional; they can help you see a different solution than the one that ends everything.",
