    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not a trap though. it's just the reality of how much space i take up. i'm just a sinkhole for their energy and money. if i just stopped being a factor in their lives, they could finally have a real chance at being happy. wouldn't that be the most selfless thing i could actually do for them? to just get out of the way?",
